3- (Saddam = Guild Leader of Phantom Knights) they develop their WoMD and bully their neighbors more than they already are.<br>
4- (Saddam = Guild Leader of Burn) they continue to try to rebuild their nation.  Due to Saddam's ArcheType AA skill boosting his charisma he continues to lead his country and become extremely wealthy.  Eventually he dies and one of his sons takes over.  2 generations of heirs from now, one of these heirs was PLed and is totally gimp and the people of Iraq finally revolt and seek out a non-gimp Guild Leader.<br>
